LoadingScreen/Help08=Try to have at least one Hero near every battle to maximize your team's experience gain.
LoadingScreen/Help09=Death timers increase as the match progresses.  Be careful, dying in the late-game can have a heavy cost.

LoadingScreen/Help13=A blue "Eye" appears over your Hero when you are hidden from enemy sight. A red "Eye" means you have been revealed.
LoadingScreen/Help14=Many abilities can Slow or Root your Hero, making it difficult or impossible to move.
LoadingScreen/Help15=Some Abilities can Stun or Silence your Hero, preventing you from using your Abilities.
LoadingScreen/Help16=Abilities that make a Hero "Unstoppable" remove or prevent most negative effects like Roots, Slows and Stuns.

LoadingScreen/Help19=If the enemy team hits level 10 before you, be careful! They have their Heroic abilities and can more easily win fights.

LoadingScreen/Help26=The enemy team gains experience each time your Hero dies. Retreat when you're low on health and heal up before fighting again.

LoadingScreen/Help36=Each point of Armor reduces the damage a Hero takes by 1%. For example: 10 Armor reduces damage by 10%.
